Package com.complexible.common.openrdf.query

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BooleanQueryResult
    An analog to TupleQueryResult and GraphQueryResult, this represents the result to a Boolean/Ask query.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter
    BooleanQueryResultWriter base for creating custom writer implementations which throws UnsupportedOperationException exceptions for the non-boolean result format methods which are incorrectly in the QueryResultWriter interface.
    AbstractQueryResult<T>
    AbstractQueryResultWriter
    More useful base for creating custom QueryResultWriter implementations.

    Collection of utility methods for working with the OpenRdf Sesame Query API.
